OL,3,CEx-chief of borders David Neal said he
OL,4,Cwas fired 'for doing his job'
OL,6,FThe former borders watchdog David Neal
OL,7,Ftold MPs he was fired "for doing (his)
OL,8,Fjob" amid claims he breached the terms
OL,9,Fof his appointment.
OL,11,FMr Neal said Tuesday that the means by
OL,12,Fwhich he was fired were "shocking"
OL,13,Fafter he became embroiled in a row
OL,14,Fwith the Home Office for saying the UK
OL,15,FBorder Force had failed to check
OL,16,Fhundreds of private jets arriving at
OL,17,FLondon City airport.
