OL,3,CEx-chief of borders David Neal said he
OL,4,Cwas fired 'for doing his job'
OL,6,FHe told the committee: "I now know
OL,7,Fthat the Home Office, so the
OL,8,Fministers, supported my reappointment,
OL,9,Fmy extension, my reappointment. And
OL,10,Fthe Home Secretary supported my
OL,11,Freappointment.
OL,13,F"That reappointment process was sent
OL,14,Fto the Cabinet Office and that was
OL,15,Fsent on to No 10 and it was turned
OL,16,Fdown by No 10.
OL,18,F"So, I've no idea why it was turned
OL,19,Fdown by No 10."
