OL,4,Cwas fired 'for doing his job'
OL,6,FMr Neal also denied a suggestion by
OL,7,FHome Secretary James Cleverly that he
OL,8,Fhad been afforded the opportunity to
OL,9,Freapply for his role, telling MPs that
OL,10,Fwas "not the case".
OL,12,FMr Neal's tenure as the independent
OL,13,Fborders watchdog was due to end on
OL,14,FMarch 21 and he claimed No 10 had
OL,15,Fblocked his reappointment before he
OL,16,Fwas ultimately fired.
OL,18,FMr Neal told the MPs he had been fired
OL,19,Fin a Microsoft Teams meeting held
OL,20,Fonline.
